room_title: Escape room "Save the White House II" by Room Escape DC in Washington, D.C.
room_description: A group of renegade hackers have taken control of the United States nuclear arsenal and have ordered a strike on several major US cities…you’d think it’d be more secure than that, but that’s not the point. As the secret service’s ranking agents, it falls upon you to disarm the attack before tragedy strikes. Use your knowledge and skills to get the job done.
